miered on October 26, 2018. A ten-episode third season was released on March 5, 2020.<ref>{{cite web |last=Elfring |first=Matt |title=Here's What's New to Netflix in March 2020: Castlevania Season 3, More Movies, TV Shows, and Originals |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/heres-whats-new-to-netflix-in-march-2020-castlevan/1100-6473892/ |website=[[GameSpot]] |access-date=6 March 2020 |date=March 5, 2020}}</ref> The final season, consisting of 10 episodes, was released on May 13, 2021.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/castlevania-season-4-review-netflix|title=Castlevania: Season 4 Review|last=Schedeen|first=Jesse|website=[[IGN]]|date=May 13, 2021|access-date=July 12, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513161857/https://www.ign.com/articles/castlevania-season-4-review-netflix|archive-date=May 13, 2021|url-status=live}}</ref>

